sequenceDiagram
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions
    participant OAuth as Google OAuth
    participant CWS as Chrome Web Store API v2

    Dev->>GH: Create release (tag: v1.0.1)
    GH->>GHA: Trigger prod-upload-and-publish workflow

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over GHA: Pre-check Job
        GHA->>GH: Does tag beta-v1.0.1 exist?
        alt Beta tag missing
            GH-->>GHA: ❌ Not found
            GHA-->>Dev: Workflow fails
        else Beta tag exists
            GH-->>GHA: ✅ Found
        end
        GHA->>GH: Do both tags point to same commit?
        alt Commit mismatch
            GH-->>GHA: ❌ Different commits
            GHA-->>Dev: Workflow fails
        else Same commit
            GH-->>GHA: ✅ Matched
        end
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over GHA: Build Job
        GHA->>GHA: Checkout code
        GHA->>GHA: Verify tag version matches .env version
        alt Version mismatch
            GHA-->>Dev: ❌ Workflow fails
        end
        GHA->>GHA: yarn install
        GHA->>GHA: Run build-extension.sh<br/>(load .env → Vite build → zip)
        GHA->>GHA: Upload artifact
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note over GHA: Upload Job
        GHA->>OAuth: curl POST /token (refresh token)
        OAuth-->>GHA: Access token
        GHA->>CWS: curl POST /items/:upload (extension-dist.zip)
        CWS-->>GHA: Upload success
    end

    alt Any job fails
        rect rgb(255, 235, 235)
            Note over GHA: Cleanup Job
            GHA->>GH: Delete release via GitHub API
            GHA->>GH: Delete tag via GitHub API
        end
    end
